The British government
has chartered a plane...

26
00:02:55,008 --> 00:02:55,614
Hey!

27
00:02:55,639 --> 00:02:57,919
- ...which will arrive in three days' time.
- Hello. Hello!

28
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:58,913
One moment, please.

29
00:02:58,937 --> 00:02:59,822
